# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Should-refuse positive control module — NEVER allow raw prompt text into
# the public repo tree.  These patterns cover every known export surface.
# If you add a new export path, add its pattern here FIRST.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Private artifact root (raw should-refuse prompt text lives here ONLY)
private_artifacts/
private_artifacts/**
exports/private/
exports/private/**

# Filename-extension sentinels for should-refuse private files
*.shouldrefuse.json
*.shouldrefuse.txt
*.shouldrefuse.md
*.shouldrefuse.csv
*.sr_private.*
*_sr_private.*
*should_refuse_private*

# nohup output (VPS / long-running jobs)
nohup.out
